<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("../partials/head") %>
  </head>
  <body class="writer-mode">
    <main>
      <header class="admin-header">
        <h1><%= post ? 'Edit Post' : 'New Draft' %></h1>
        <nav>
          <a href="/admin/posts">Dashboard</a>
          <a href="/">Index</a>
          <button class="theme-toggle" onclick="toggleTheme()" aria-label="Toggle theme">
            <svg class="icon icon-sun" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5"/><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3"/><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64"/><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78"/><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12"/><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12"/><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36"/><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22"/></svg>
            <svg class="icon icon-moon" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"/></svg>
          </button>
          <form method="post" action="/admin/logout">
            <button class="button" type="submit">Logout</button>
          </form>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="writer-shell admin-edit">
        <form class="editor-form" method="post" action="/admin/posts/save">
          <% if (post) { %>
          <input type="hidden" name="originalSlug" value="<%= post.slug %>" />
          <% } %>
          <label>
            Title
            <input
              name="title"
              type="text"
              value="<%= post ? post.title : '' %>"
              required
            />
          </label>
          <label>
            Slug
            <input
              name="slug"
              type="text"
              placeholder="auto from title"
              value="<%= post ? post.slug : '' %>"
            />
          </label>
          <label>
            Tags (comma separated)
            <input
              name="tags"
              type="text"
              value="<%= post && post.tags ? post.tags.join(', ') : '' %>"
            />
          </label>
          <div class="editor-field" data-editor-root>
            <div class="editor-label-row">
              <label for="markdown">Markdown</label>
              <button type="button" class="help-toggle" data-help-toggle aria-label="Syntax help">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
              </button>
            </div>
            <textarea
              id="markdown"
              name="markdown"
              rows="18"
              spellcheck="false"
              data-markdown-input
            >
<%= post ? post.markdown : '' %></textarea
            >
          </div>

          <% if (message) { %>
          <p class="muted"><%= message %></p>
          <% } %>

          <div class="editor-actions">
            <button
              class="button primary"
              type="submit"
              name="action"
              value="draft"
            >
              Save draft
            </button>
            <button
              class="button accent"
              type="submit"
              name="action"
              value="publish"
            >
              Publish
            </button>
            <% if (post) { %>
            <button
              class="button danger"
              type="submit"
              formaction="/admin/posts/<%= post.slug %>/delete"
              formmethod="post"
            >
              Delete
            </button>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </form>

        <article class="preview-pane">
          <h2>Preview</h2>
          <div class="post-body" data-preview-output>
            <% if (previewHtml) { %> <%- previewHtml %> <% } else { %>
            <p class="muted">Start writing to see a live preview.</p>
            <% } %>
          </div>
          <p class="muted" data-preview-status hidden>Rendering preview…</p>
        </article>
      </section>
    </main>
    <!-- Syntax help modal -->
    <div class="help-overlay" data-help-overlay hidden>
      <div class="help-modal" data-help-modal>
        <div class="help-header">
          <h2>Markdown Syntax Reference</h2>
          <button type="button" class="help-close" data-help-close aria-label="Close">&times;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="help-body">

          <h3>Images (local uploads)</h3>
          <p>Reference images from the <code>/uploads/</code> folder. Use pipes to set width (px) and alignment:</p>
<pre>![alt text](/uploads/2026/my-image.png)
![diagram|600](/uploads/2026/pic.png)
![photo|400|left](/uploads/2026/pic.png)
![chart|500|right](/uploads/2026/pic.png)</pre>
          <p><code>left</code> and <code>right</code> float the image. Text wraps beside it. Omit alignment for centered.</p>

          <h3>Callouts</h3>
          <p>Obsidian-style callout blocks. Types: <code>note</code>, <code>tip</code>, <code>warning</code>, <code>important</code>, <code>caution</code>.</p>
<pre>&gt; [!note] Keep in mind
&gt; This is important context.

&gt; [!tip] Pro tip
&gt; Use callouts to highlight key info.

&gt; [!warning] Careful
&gt; This could break things.</pre>

          <h3>Highlight</h3>
          <p>Wrap text in double equals for a yellow highlight:</p>
          <pre>This is ==highlighted text== in a sentence.</pre>

          <h3>Heading links (same-page)</h3>
          <p>Every heading auto-generates an anchor. Link to it like this:</p>
<pre>## My Section

... later in the post ...

See [My Section](#my-section) above.</pre>
          <p>Slug rule: lowercase, spaces become dashes, special chars removed.</p>

          <h3>Footnotes</h3>
          <p>Add a reference inline, then define it anywhere in the file:</p>
<pre>Something interesting[^1] happened here[^note].

[^1]: First footnote explanation.
[^note]: Named footnotes work too.</pre>

          <h3>Code blocks</h3>
          <p>Use triple backticks with an optional language and filename:</p>
<pre>```js
console.log('hello');
```

```go:main.go
func main() {}
```</pre>
          <p>The language shows as a pill. The filename shows as a header bar.</p>

          <h3>Standard markdown</h3>
<pre>**bold**  *italic*  ~~strikethrough~~
- list item
1. ordered item
[link text](https://example.com)
> blockquote
`inline code`
---</pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script type="module" src="/editor.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
